 <html:ol
xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
    
 <html:li
style="list-style-type: &quot;iv. &quot;">
      The cartesian product of two unramified morphisms is unramified.
    </html:li>

    
 <html:li
style="list-style-type: &quot;v. &quot;">
      If <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[gf]]></fr:tex> is unramified then so too is <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex>.
    </html:li>

    
 <html:li
style="list-style-type: &quot;vi. &quot;">
      If <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex> is unramified then so too is <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f_\mathrm {red}]]></fr:tex>.
    </html:li>

  </html:ol>
</fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree><fr:tree
